1226   0761             ; after adding the new directory's information to its parent directory's list
1227   0761             ; we need to now enter the new directory, and to it add two new directories!
1228   0761             ; which directories do we need to add ? '..' and '.' are the directories needed.
1229   0761             ; importantly, note that these two new directories are only entries in the list
1230   0761             ; and do not have actual physical entries in the disk as real directories.
1231   0761             ; i.e. they only exist as list entries in the new directory created so that
1232   0761             ; the new directory can reference its parent and itself.
1233   0761             ; We need to add both '..' and '.'
1234   0761             ; this first section is for '..' and on the section below we do the same for '.'
